      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      277.6,
      558.36,
      290.88
    ],
    "text": "On the day of the incident Yesurasan, on hearing screams of a woman, ran to the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      305.2,
      558.23,
      318.48
    ],
    "text": "place where the screams emanated and saw the Accused-Appellant grappling with a woman.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      332.8,
      557.89,
      346.08
    ],
    "text": "On hearing the shouts of Yesurasan, a toddy tapper named Marrie and his son Tiron Ranjith",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      360.4,
      222.05,
      373.68
    ],
    "text": "came to the scene.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      415.62,
      558.09,
      428.9
    ],
    "text": "When his son came to scene, he saw a person hiding behind a parapet wall. He chased",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman",
      "Times New Roman,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      443.22,
      560.84,
      456.5
    ],
    "text": "after this person as he ran away from the scene of offence and attacked him with a club.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      470.82,
      558.34,
      484.1
    ],
    "text": "However he says he could not identifying him as there was mud on his face. He says that this",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      498.42,
      555.38,
      511.7
    ],
    "text": "person was a dark short person. But according to Identification Parade notes the Accused-",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      526.02,
      558.18,
      539.3
    ],
    "text": "Appellant is a 5 and \u00bd feet tall person. The Accused-Appellant was arrested 11 months after",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      553.65,
      555.26,
      566.93
    ],
    "text": "the incident. Then an identification parade was held in order to identify the Accused-",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      581.25,
      558.27,
      594.53
    ],
